{"tid":722138,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【世界盃】中國無緣賽事　內地學者：正好說明人民生活水平提高","createTime":"2018-06-29T08:36:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-29T13:15:28.000Z","uid":9116,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2bd99cb96a8af27d702d68890807411b8694dcae","tid":722138,"uid":9116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T08:36:45.000Z","msg":"經中國無緣今屆世界盃，有內地學者就從國民生活水平解釋，認為國家隊無法晉身世界盃，正好說明中國人民的生活水平提高了，只有富人的孩子踢足球，但不會長踢得久，故中國足球發展後繼無人也屬意料中事。<br />\n<br />\n新浪體育昨日播放的《V觀世界杯》中，邀請中國人民大學法學博士、國際關系專家儲殷，從其他角度解讀今屆世界盃。儲殷在節目開初先分析多個隊伍在分組賽的表現，指即使有明星坐鎮的國家亦因欠缺默契，而變得與被認為較弱的國家實力相當。<br />\n<br />\n他其後更提到中國足球的「痛處」，形容中國隊無緣世界盃，正好說明了中國人民的生活水平提高，「在中國踢足球都是有錢孩子，上足球班多貴啊，窮人孩子無法踢球，沒有場地，沒有草皮；富人孩子掏錢踢球不會玩下去，中國足球後繼無人很正常」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180629/s00006/1530244904623\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180629%2Fs00006%2F1530244904623&d=Zp%2FOZbqkgEy4%2Bn%2FMoifyyLDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=dd54e85b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180629%2Fs00006%2F1530244904623&h=e3ce2bcb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180629/s00006/1530244904623</a>"},{"pid":"1e19f65a92613e0fc838c4f071ed2c02adb2214b","tid":722138,"uid":91556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T08:44:47.000Z","msg":"又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c616ab87398483efcacd95ce789407af3bbf6207","tid":722138,"uid":9116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T08:44:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c16f29c5341adc9723ce5e040ee0762fc831b1da","tid":722138,"uid":48843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-